Package: Morefi
Type: Package
Title: Morphological Relationships Fitted by Robust Regression 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hugo Aguirre-Villaseñor
Maintainer: Hugo Aguirre-Villaseñor <hugo.aguirre@inapesca.gob.mx>
Description: It is a methodological package developed to carry out the
    analyzes of the article: Aguirre-Villaseñor et al. (IN PREPARATION).
    For this purpose, some functions and a vignette were created to explain 
    the process step by step. The tables and figures were personalized. The
    lmrob() and nlrob() from robustbase (version 0.99-2), is used to perform
    robust regression.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)    
